This remnant of virgin cypress forest runs northward to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taoyuan County 's</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">Mt. Lala</ENAMEX> and to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Chilan</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Ilan County</ENAMEX> .
This great wall of trees acts as a vital " safety valve , " regulating the flow of water into <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">the Shihmen Reservoir</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">the Tanshui River</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">the Lanyang River</ENAMEX> , on which millions of people in northern <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> depend for the water they drink .
