" The trees have been growing by themselves for tens of thousands of years , so why would they need human help for their saplings to grow ? "
In response to this situation a popular movement sprang up to push for the establishment of a " cypress forest national park , " in the hope that with national park status , the last remaining virgin <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> yellow cypress forest could be saved .
