A future for the cypresses ?
At the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Atayal</ENAMEX> village of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Chenhsipao</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Hsinchu County</ENAMEX> , by <ENAMEX TYPE="TIME">three in the afternoon</ENAMEX> the clouds rolling in from afar have quietly slipped over the ridges and covered the whole mountainside where the cypress trees grow .
